<topic id="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view">
  <title>Relax NG Outline View</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Relax NG schemas<indexterm>Outline view</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view for Relax NG schemas presents a list with the
      patterns that appear in the diagram in both the <xref
        href="relax-ng-schema-diagram-full-model-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-full-model-view"
          ><uicontrol>Full Model View</uicontrol></xref> and <xref
        href="relax-ng-schema-diagram-logical-model-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-logical-model-view"
          ><uicontrol>Logical Model View</uicontrol></xref> cases and it allows for quick access to
      a component by name. By default, it is displayed on the left side of the editor. <ph
        conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view"/></p>
    <p>
      <fig product="editor developer">
        <title>Relax NG Outline View</title>
        <image href="../img/sa_relaxng_schema_outline_view.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>
      <fig product="editorEclipse developerEclipse">
        <title>Relax NG Outline View</title>
        <image href="../img/ec_relaxng_schema_outline_view.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>This view has two modes, with the tree showing either the XML structure or the defined
      pattern (components) collected from the current document. By default, the
        <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view presents the components. </p>
    <p>When the <uicontrol><image href="../img/TagsComponents16.png" id="image_vlg_kfg_ks"/>Show
        components</uicontrol> option is selected in the <ph product="editor developer"
            ><uicontrol><image href="../img/Settings16.png" id="image_eqk_zqm_ks"
          />Settings</uicontrol> menu on the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view toolbar</ph><ph
        product="editorEclipse developerEclipse"><uicontrol>View menu</uicontrol> on the
          <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view action bar</ph>, the following option is
      available:</p>
    <p>
      <dl>
        <dlentry id="outline_show_components">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/TagsComponents16.png" id="image_n5b_cgt_tr"/>Show XML
              structure</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Shows the XML structure of the current document in a tree-like manner.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
    <p>The following actions are available in the <ph product="editor developer"><uicontrol><image
            href="../img/Settings16.png" id="image_hgq_dhg_ks"/>Settings</uicontrol> menu on the
          <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view toolbar</ph><ph
        product="editorEclipse developerEclipse"><uicontrol>View menu</uicontrol> on the
          <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view action bar</ph> when the <uicontrol><image
          href="../img/TagsComponents16.png" id="image_v2n_gfg_ks"/>Show XML structure</uicontrol>
      option is selected:</p>
    <p>
      <dl>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Filter returns exact matches</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>The text filter of the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view returns only exact
            matches.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/CaretUpdateOff16.png" id="image_l35_sft_tr"/>Selection
              update on cursor move</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Allows a synchronization between <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view and schema
            diagram. The selected view from the diagram will be also selected in the
              <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/TagsComponents16.png" id="image_gql_bgt_tr"/>Show
              components</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Shows the defined pattern collected from the current document.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/outline-flat-presentation-mode">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/outline_show_comments">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/show_element_name">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/comments_sjow_text">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/outline_show_attributes">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/outline-configure-displayed-attrs">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
    <p>The following contextual menu actions are also available in the
        <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view when the <uicontrol><image
          href="../img/TagsComponents16.png" id="image_dvn_cjg_ks"/>Show XML structure</uicontrol>
      option is selected in the <ph product="editor developer"><uicontrol><image
            href="../img/Settings16.png" id="image_evn_cjg_ks"/>Settings</uicontrol> menu</ph><ph
        product="editorEclipse developerEclipse"><uicontrol>View menu</uicontrol></ph>:</p>
    <p>
      <dl>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Append Child</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Displays a list of elements that you can insert as children of the current
            element.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Insert Before</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Displays a list of elements that you can insert as siblings of the current element,
            before the current element.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Insert After</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Displays a list of elements that you can insert as siblings of the current element,
            after the current element.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Attribute16.gif"/>Edit Attributes</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens a dialog box that allows you to edit the attributes of the currently selected
            component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/ToggleComment16.png" id="image_bsr_brd_cs"/>Toggle
              Comment</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Comments/uncomments the currently selected element.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/SearchReferences16.png" placement="inline"
                id="image_a41_5jg_ks"/>Search references</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Searches for the references of the currently selected component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Search references in</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Searches for the references of the currently selected component in the context of a
            scope that you define.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/ComponentDependencies16.png" id="image_q2l_j3t_tr"
              />Component dependencies</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens the <xref href="rng-component-dependencies.dita#rng-component-dependencies"
                ><uicontrol>Component Dependencies</uicontrol> view</xref> that displays the
            dependencies of the currently selected component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RenameXSLResource16.png" id="image_rpj_mv1_5r"/>Rename
              Component in</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Renames the currently selected component in the context of a scope that you
            define.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Cut16.png" id="image_u1f_hz1_5r"/>Cut</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Cuts the currently selected component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Copy16.png" id="image_x2z_mst_tr"
            />Copy</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Copies the currently selected component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RemoveSelected16.gif" placement="inline"
                id="image_b41_5jg_ks"/>Delete</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Deletes the currently selected component.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol product="developer editor"><image href="../img/ExpandAll16.png"
                placement="inline" id="image_lny_prd_cs"/>Expand More</uicontrol><uicontrol
              product="developerEclipse editorEclipse"><image href="../img/ExpandAll16.png"
                placement="inline" id="image_ywc_f1j_cs"/>Expand All</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Expands the structure of a component in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/CollapseAll16.png" id="image_yl1_r3t_tr"/>Collapse
              All</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Collapses the structure of all the component in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol>
            view.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
    <p
      conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/outliner-filter-box"/>
    
